            "Rozpoczynam trening HerBERT (3 epok)...\n",
            "\n",
            "Epoka 1/3 | Train Loss: 0.5815 | Train Acc: 0.7097 | Val Loss: 0.5205 | Val Acc: 0.7493 | Val F1: 0.7135\n",
            "Epoka 2/3 | Train Loss: 0.4869 | Train Acc: 0.7684 | Val Loss: 0.5166 | Val Acc: 0.7540 | Val F1: 0.7455\n",
            "Epoka 3/3 | Train Loss: 0.3814 | Train Acc: 0.8339 | Val Loss: 0.5533 | Val Acc: 0.7587 | Val F1: 0.7513\n"
          ]
